/****** Object:  Table [dbo].[Item]    Script Date: 3/9/2021 12:44:37 AM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE TABLE [dbo].[Item](
	[ID] [int] IDENTITY(1,1) NOT NULL,
	[Barcode] [char](16) NOT NULL,
	[Name] [nvarchar](200) NULL,
	[Description] [nvarchar](400) NULL,
	[Shelf] [nvarchar](50) NULL,
	[PurchasePrice] [decimal](18, 2) NULL,
	[SalePrice] [decimal](18, 2) NULL,
	[PiecesPerPack] [int] NULL,
	[SalePricePerPiece] [decimal](18, 2) NULL,
	[OtherBonus] [decimal](18, 0) NULL,
	[ManufacturerID] [int] NULL,
	[ItemTypeID] [int] NULL,
	[Packing] [nvarchar](50) NULL,
	[PackSize] [int] NULL,
	[GenericName] [nvarchar](60) NULL,
	[PurchasePercentage] [int] NULL,
	[SalePercentage] [int] NULL,
	[TotalStock] [int] NULL,
	[LooseQuantitySold] [int] NULL,
	[SpecialDiscount] [int] NULL,
	[StripPerPack] [int] NULL,
	[TabPerStrip] [int] NULL,
	[TotalItemPerPack]  AS ([StripPerPack]*[TabPerStrip]),
	[LowStockQuantity] [int] NULL,
	[CriticalLowStockQuantity] [int] NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [PK_Item] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	[ID] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]
GO

	[TotalAfterPercentage] [decimal](18, 2) NULL,

	[Arears] [decimal](18, 2) NULL,
	[SpecialDiscount] [int] NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [PK_Sale] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	[ID] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]

GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE TABLE [dbo].[SaleItem](
	[ID] [int] IDENTITY(1,1) NOT NULL,
	[SaleID] [int] NULL,
	[ItemID] [int] NULL,
	[SalePercentage] [int] NULL,
	[Quantity] [int] NULL,
	[LoosePack] [char](2) NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [PK_SaleItem] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	[ID] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]
GO
/****** Object:  View [dbo].[ItemSaleItemSale]    Script Date: 3/9/2021 12:44:37 AM ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE VIEW [dbo].[ItemSaleItemSale]
AS
SELECT        dbo.Item.ID, dbo.Item.Name, dbo.Sale.ID AS Expr1, dbo.SaleItem.ID AS Expr2, dbo.Sale.DateOfSale, dbo.Sale.TotalBeforePercentage, dbo.Sale.TotalAfterPercentage, dbo.Sale.AmountPaid, dbo.Sale.Arears, 
                         dbo.SaleItem.SalePercentage, dbo.SaleItem.Quantity, dbo.SaleItem.ItemID, dbo.Item.SalePrice, dbo.Sale.SpecialDiscount
FROM            dbo.Item INNER JOIN
                         dbo.Sale ON dbo.Item.ID = dbo.Sale.ID INNER JOIN
                         dbo.SaleItem ON dbo.Item.ID = dbo.SaleItem.ItemID AND dbo.Sale.ID = dbo.SaleItem.SaleID

GO

EXEC sys.sp_addextendedproperty @name=N'MS_DiagramPane1', @value=N'[0E232FF0-B466-11cf-A24F-00AA00A3EFFF, 1.00]
Begin DesignProperties = 
   Begin PaneConfigurations = 
      Begin PaneConfiguration = 0
         NumPanes = 4
         Configuration = "(H (1[40] 4[20] 2[20] 3) )"
      End
      Begin PaneConfiguration = 1
         NumPanes = 3
         Configuration = "(H (1 [50] 4 [25] 3))"
      End
      Begin PaneConfiguration = 2
         NumPanes = 3
         Configuration = "(H (1 [50] 2 [25] 3))"
      End
      Begin PaneConfiguration = 3
         NumPanes = 3
         Configuration = "(H (4 [30] 2 [40] 3))"
      End
      Begin PaneConfiguration = 4
         NumPanes = 2
         Configuration = "(H (1 [56] 3))"
      End
      Begin PaneConfiguration = 5
         NumPanes = 2
         Configuration = "(H (2 [66] 3))"
      End
      Begin PaneConfiguration = 6
         NumPanes = 2
